      "explanation_en": "Momentum investing is a strategy that buys stocks already trending upward, betting that strong recent performance continues in the near term. Tools like RSI (measuring speed of price moves) and MACD (tracking trend direction and strength) help identify stocks in a 'momentum sweet spot' \u2014 rising but not yet overbought. Today's top picks like LWLG and MARA exemplify this: price above their moving average, MACD confirming the trend, and RSI in the bullish-but-not-extended zone.",
